### ==========================================
### KodaX API Testing Flow
### ==========================================
### Usage Instructions:
### 1. Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code.
### 2. Follow the steps below in order.
### 3. Replace the variables manually if your REST Client doesn't support automatic variable extraction.
### ==========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/api
# Replace these with actual values after running the respective requests
@token1 = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2OWZjNDY5NWQ1ZWE5NzljZmJhOWZhMDciLCJpYXQiOjE3NzgxNDA4MjEsImV4cCI6MTc3ODc0NTYyMX0.9uceCbe8ciLjmxv2UIhdaa4MuUXCd6mx3wpFdHG4Crs
@token2 = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2OWZjNDc0ZmQ1ZWE5NzljZmJhOWZhMGYiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzgxNDEwMDcsImV4cCI6MTc3ODc0NTgwN30.ylcUgCDglvNj9X47oK5ZP3uFfsN9Vpm-DlJuLvXUVUQ
@roomId = 5623de27-3c59-4be4-a75f-e8d6337232aa
@user2Id =69fc474fd5ea979cfba9fa0f

### ==========================================
### STEP 1: AUTHENTICATION
### ==========================================


###
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "OwnerUser",
    "password": "securepassword",
    "email": "owner@mail.com"
}

### 1b. Login User 1 (Copy the token from cookies/response to @token1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "owner@mail.com",
    "password": "securepassword"
}

### 1c. Check Profile (Verifies Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### ==========================================
### STEP 2: ROOM CREATION & MANAGEMENT (As Owner)
### ==========================================

### 2a. Create a Room (Copy payload.roomId to @roomId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/room/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test Collaboration Room",
    "description": "A room to test all features",
    "language": "javascript",
    "visibility": "private"
}

### 2b. Get My Rooms (Verify room was created)
GET {{baseUrl}}/room/my-rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 2c. Update Room Settings
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "maxUsers": 5,
    "allowGuests": true
}

### ==========================================
### STEP 3: SECOND USER (The Guest)
### ==========================================

### 3a. Register User 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "GuestUser",
    "password": "securepassword",
    "email": "guest@mail.com"
}

### 3b. Login User 2 (Copy user ID to @user2Id and token to @token2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "guest@mail.com",
    "password": "securepassword"
}

### ==========================================
### STEP 4: JOINING PROCESS
### ==========================================

### 4a. Guest searches for public rooms (Should be empty since we made it private)
GET {{baseUrl}}/room/search?q=Test

### 4b. Guest requests to join the private room
POST {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}/request-join
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 4c. Owner checks pending requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 4d. Owner approves Guest (Using User 2's ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}/approve/{{user2Id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 4e. Guest fetches the room details (Should now work since they are approved)
GET {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### ==========================================
### STEP 5: CODE & CHAT OPERATIONS
### ==========================================

### 5a. Get Initial Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/code/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 5b. Update Code (By Guest)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/code/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "console.log('Hello from Guest!');",
    "language": "javascript"
}

### 5c. Get Chat Messages (Should be empty initially)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### ==========================================
### STEP 6: ADVANCED ROOM MANAGEMENT
### ==========================================

### 6a. Owner promotes Guest to Moderator
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}/promote/{{user2Id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 6b. Owner demotes Guest back to Member
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}/demote/{{user2Id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 6c. Owner deletes the room
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/room/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
